# Day 17 – Automotive Fuel Analytics Dashboard

## Overview

Today I built an Automotive Fuel Analytics Dashboard that analyzes vehicle fuel efficiency, operating costs, maintenance expenses, emissions, and E85 fuel viability using CSV-based data analytics.

The project transforms raw vehicle fuel data into an interactive dashboard built with pure HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and SVG visualizations.

---

## Objective

Create a data-driven dashboard capable of:

- Comparing Petrol, Diesel, CNG, EV, and E85 fuels
- Calculating fuel cost efficiency
- Measuring CO₂ emissions impact
- Evaluating maintenance expenses
- Performing vehicle age analysis
- Assessing E85 fuel feasibility through a custom scoring model

